# Tally connector debug/response dumps may contain raw party names,
# GSTINs, addresses. Filenames themselves often leak client identity
# (e.g. tally_receipts_debug_M-TRADING_CO_.xml). Block all XML in the
# connector dir — TDL templates live as Python strings, not files.
credfloat-assignment/connector/*.xml
*_debug_*.xml

